== 退役 ==
1956年奥运会结束后，年仅15岁的利奇决定从竞技游泳事业退休。作为本迪戈历史上首位奥运奖牌得主，她在返回故乡时受到热烈款待。据利奇回忆，[[奥运村|奥运村]]的生活对她来说很不寻常，除了面对大量人流和参与奥运的压力外，这也是她首次远离故乡。医生认为她在比赛前过分紧张，所以支持她退役。利奇身形高大，接下来一度在墨尔本当模特儿，但不久后就返回本迪戈经营家族珠宝生意。<ref name="Howell-1986" />{{rp|135}}父亲在20世纪70年代去世后，她成为家族生意的主心骨，之后又把业务转给儿子负责<ref name="jewel" />。

利奇与米奇·托伊（{{lang|en|Mitch Tuohy}}）结婚后生有两子<ref name="jewel" />，分别起名亚当（{{lang|en|Adam}}）和特洛伊（{{lang|en|Troy}}）<ref name="fighter">{{cite news | date = 2003-12-14 | newspaper = Herald Sun | title = 'You have to be a fighter' | at = News1 – First section}}</ref>，她不希望孩子走上竞技游泳之路，担心比赛压力的影响。退役后，她对体育竞技避而远之，但依旧维持健美身材和运动能力<ref name="Howell-1986" />{{rp|135}}<ref name="a249" />。此外，她还教导残障儿童学习游泳，部分学徒之后代表澳大利亚参加[[特殊奥林匹克运动会|特殊奥林匹克运动会]]<ref name="bendigo" />。

退役后，利奇通过志愿工作继续参与奥林匹克运动。1999年7月，她和澳大利亚当时最年长的男子兼[[第一次世界大战|一战]]老兵[[杰克·洛基特|杰克·洛基特]]（{{lang|en|Jack Lockett}}）获得邀请，参加2000年7月[[奥林匹克圣火|奥林匹克圣火]]传递到本迪戈的倒计时庆典<ref>{{cite news | date = 1999-07-29 | work = Australian Associated Press | title = Diary for Thursday, July 29, 1999}}</ref>。2001年，利奇经确诊在颈部患有[[癌症|癌瘤]]，尺寸和50分硬币接近<ref name="fighter" />。经过为期六周的放射治疗，利奇接受手术移除肿瘤<ref name="fighter" />。这段经历促使她成为[[昆士兰癌症理事会|癌症理事会]]的志愿者，向确诊患上癌症的人们伸出援手<ref name="fighter" />。2003年2月，她致电安慰四次获奥运金牌、正处[[脑溢血|脑溢血]]恢复期的[[贝蒂·卡思伯特|贝蒂·卡思伯特]]（{{lang|en|Betty Cuthbert}}）<ref>{{cite news | last = Reed | first = Ron | date = 2003-02-26 | newspaper = Herald Sun | title = Golden moment beckons Betty | page = 76, Sport section | quote = As Cuthbert is showing us the big bag of get-well cards and expressing her gratitude for the way people have rallied around, the phone rings. It is Faith Leech, who was a swimming gold medallist in 1956 and has remained a friend. She just wants to touch base, to make sure everything's OK.}}</ref>。2006年10月，利奇同1956年的队友[[约翰·德维特_(游泳运动员)|约翰·德维特]]（{{lang|en|John Devitt}}）一起推出[[澳大利亚邮政|澳大利亚邮政]]发行的“墨尔本奥运会50年”系列邮票<ref>{{cite news |date=2006-10-31 |work=MediaNet Press Releases |title=Australia Post marks time in Melbourne |accessdate=2009-10-02 |url=http://www.auspost.com.au/BCP/0,1467,CH4397~MO19,00.html |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091002182116/http://www.auspost.com.au/BCP/0%2C1467%2CCH4397~MO19%2C00.html |archivedate=2009-10-02 }}</ref>。

2013年9月14日，费斯·利奇在家中去世，享年72岁<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160323195953/http://www.bendigoadvertiser.com.au/story/1777686/bendigo-mourns-olympic-gold-medallist/ | url = http://www.bendigoadvertiser.com.au/story/1777686/bendigo-mourns-olympic-gold-medallist/ | title = Bendigo mourns Olympic gold medallist | newspaper = Bendigo Advertiser | date = 2013-09-15 | accessdate = 2016-09-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-23 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | title = Australian Olympic Medalist Faith Leech Passes Away at 72 | url = https://swimswam.com/swimming-australia-mourning-passing-olympian-faith-leech/ | publisher = Swim Swam | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160529030616/https://swimswam.com/swimming-australia-mourning-passing-olympian-faith-leech/ | date = 2013-09-17 | accessdate = 2016-09-30 | archivedate = 2016-05-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。2014年，利奇入选[[悉尼国际水上运动中心|悉尼奥林匹克公园水上运动中心]]的“冠军之路”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.aquaticcentre.com.au/attractions/path_of_champions | title = Path of Champions | publisher = Sydney Olympic Park Aquatic Centre | accessdate = 2016-09-30 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325200604/http://www.aquaticcentre.com.au/attractions/path_of_champions | archivedate = 2016-03-25 }}</ref>。

